---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — Nexus by AiForStartups"
  description="Terms of service for Nexus, the operations OS for e-commerce teams."
  canonical="https://aiforstartups.io/terms/"
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-32 pb-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm mb-10" style="color: #8888a0;">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8888a0;">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using the Nexus platform, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws. If you do not agree, do not use the service.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Service Description</h2>
        <p>Nexus is a multi-tenant operations platform for e-commerce businesses. We provide tools for order management, inventory, customer communication, CRM, shipping, and analytics.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You may not use Nexus for any illegal activity, to send spam, or to violate WhatsApp Business policies. You are responsible for all activity on your account.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Data Ownership</h2>
        <p>You retain ownership of your data. We do not claim any rights to your business data, customer information, or content you upload to the platform.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Service Availability</h2>
        <p>We target 99.9% uptime on Pro and Enterprise plans. Free plan services are provided on a best-effort basis. Scheduled maintenance will be communicated in advance.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms, contact us via <a href="https://wa.me/201040003090" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs" style="color: #444458;"><!-- TODO: Complete full terms of service with legal counsel --></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
